reviewText: Excellent hentai parody of Sailor Moon. I had fun with this one.

Well this movie is a great movie for my collection, it goes great with my collection of La Blue girls.
I would recommend this movie for all people that like Anime.
Of course I mean any-one 18 years or older!

Basically, Venus 5 is an X-rated spoof of Sailor Moon--five cute girls in skimpy outfits using cool powers to defeat monsters. The major differences are that their mascot/adviser is a lecherous pervert, the monsters try to rape them, and because of child porn laws, the Venus 5 are all 18 and attending a junior college instead of 14 and in high school. The DVD contains both episodes, making it a better buy than the VHS version. The only complaint I had was with one (or should I say, two) voice actor(s)--the evil queen, in her demonic form, was dubbed with male and female voices that made it a little hard to understand what she was saying at points. Other than that, if you're not expecting too much (and why should you--this _is_ a porn parody, after all!), it's an amusing riff on the "magical girl team" theme.
